      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WINNIE MOUSE (2) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Recorded a nose win (22.00) in a Mix last time at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. FREDDY LIVE WIRE (3) recorded his 3rd career win last time at this track, scoring by 4.5 lengths (21.79). Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Likely to be in the finish. SKEDADDLE BENNY (1) was a course and distance placegetter (22.25) last time also from the same draw, finishing a 6 length third in a Grade 5. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. DON'T TELL MILLY (7) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
